      Per Owner Clarification + assessment: minimal editor sufficient. Spaarke's email pattern is mostly short replies / forwards / templated messages â€” not document-heavy formatting. Reuses Fluent v9 `Textarea` for plain text + a thin `contentEditable` wrapper for HTML.

      HTML sanitization: minimum strip `<script>` and `<iframe>` and event handlers (`onclick=`). Use a small util (or `DOMParser` + manual scrub) â€” DO NOT pull in `DOMPurify` unless already in the lib's dependencies.
    </background>
