  <steps>
    <step order="1">Check `package.json` for existing sanitization util / DOMPurify availability â€” if absent, plan a small inline `sanitizeHtml(html: string): string` util.</step>
    <step order="2">Author `BodyEditor.tsx`:
      - Props: `{ value: string; bodyFormat: 'html' | 'plaintext'; onChange: (value: string, bodyFormat: 'html' | 'plaintext') =&gt; void; disabled?: boolean }`
      - Top: `&lt;RadioGroup&gt;` with two radios "HTML" / "Plain text" â€” dispatches `onChange` with format toggle
      - Conditional render:
        * `bodyFormat='plaintext'`: `&lt;Textarea value={value} onChange={...} style={{fontFamily: tokens.fontFamilyMonospace}} aria-label="Email body, plain text" /&gt;`
