      - Toggle handler: HTMLâ†’PlainText strips tags via `el.textContent`; PlainTextâ†’HTML wraps in `&lt;p&gt;` per line</step>
    <step order="3">Inline `sanitizeHtml` util: strips `&lt;script&gt;`, `&lt;iframe&gt;`, `&lt;style&gt;`, all `on*=` attributes, `javascript:` URLs. Use `DOMParser` to parse + scrub + serialize.</step>
    <step order="4">Wire into engine's `BodyRegion` slot in `EmailComposer.tsx` â€” dispatch reducer actions for `body` + `bodyFormat`.</step>
